# Workaround Brainstormer

## Description
Workaround Brainstormer is a web application designed to facilitate the identification of workarounds based on a process description or bpmn diagram.
It`s generative AI approach helps to identify workarounds in situations where no process data is avaible.

## Features
- LLM based workaround generation
- Visual representation of the workarounds as a network graph
- Control mechanisms to lighten the generation process
    - manually add and remove corners in the graph (workarounds)

